Monterey Pop Festival.label: Monterey Pop Festival
Monterey Pop Festival.description: The Monterey International Pop Music Festival was a three-day concert event held June 16 to June 18, 1967 at the Monterey County Fairgrounds in Monterey, California. Wikipedia

Summerjam.label: Summerjam
Summerjam.description: Summerjam is Europe's biggest reggae festival. It takes places annually in July at the Fühlinger, which is a lake located in Cologne, Germany. The event usually sees an audience of between 25.000 and 30.000 people. Wikipedia

Woodstock.label: Woodstock
Woodstock.description: The Woodstock Music & Art Fair—informally, the Woodstock Festival or simply Woodstock—was a music festival, billed as "An Aquarian Exposition 3 Days of Peace & Music". Wikipedia

Appel Farm Arts and Music Festival.label: Appel Farm Arts and Music Festival
Appel Farm Arts and Music Festival.description: The Appel Farm Arts and Music Festival, is an annual one-day festival held the first Saturday in June at Appel Farm Arts and Music Center located near Elmer, in Salem County, New Jersey, USA. Wikipedia

Dockville.label: Dockville
Dockville.description: Dockville is a music and art festival on Europe's biggest river island, Hamburg's district Wilhelmsburg. It is sponsored by the German Internationale Bauausstellung and it took place for the first time in 2007. Wikipedia

Mayfair (festival).label: Mayfair
Mayfair (festival).description:
Mayfair Festival of the Arts is a multidisciplinary arts festival produced by Mayfair Inc, a 501 nonprofit organization.
The Festival is held annually at in Allentown, Pennsylvania. It has been held Memorial Day weekend since 1986. Wikipedia

Pukkelpop.label: Pukkelpop
Pukkelpop.description: Pukkelpop is an annual music festival that takes place near the city of Hasselt, Belgium in mid-to-late August. Wikipedia

Summer Darkness.label: Summer Darkness
Summer Darkness.description: Summer Darkness is an alternative music festival in the Netherlands which is being held annually since 2003 around the second weekend in August in the city of Utrecht. Over the years its popularity has grown considerably. Wikipedia

Falcon Ridge Folk Festival.label: Falcon Ridge Folk Festival
Falcon Ridge Folk Festival.description: The Falcon Ridge Folk Festival is an American annual folk-oriented music festival and dance festival formerly held at the Long Hill Farm in Hillsdale, New York, USA. Wikipedia

Homegrown Music Festival (New Zealand).label: Homegrown Music Festival
Homegrown Music Festival (New Zealand).description: Homegrown Music Festival has been held annually in Wellington, New Zealand since 2008. Wikipedia
